C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20puts%20the%20company%20in%20a%20good%20position%20to%20have%20those%20users%20frequently%20interacting%20with%20its%20AI%20tech.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20has%20already%20integrated%20AI%20into%20its%20platforms%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20spend%20billions%20on%20R%26amp%3BD.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerbergs-style-evolution-in-photos-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20looks%20poised%20to%20dominate%20the%20AI%20adoption%20race%20thanks%20to%20a%20technicality%3A%20Meta%20has%20three%20billion-plus%20captive%20users%20who%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20has%20spent%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-files-documentary-depicts-facebook-meta-ceo-life-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%20years%20building%20his%20Harvard%20dorm%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20globe-spanning%20social%20media%20empire.%20He%20now%20looks%20set%20to%20make%20Meta%20a%20clear%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20race%20to%20make%20AI%20a%20part%20of%20consumers'%20lives%20by%20simply%20cornering%20them%20into%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-spending-more-mark-zuckerberg-investors-stock-price-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20reported%20second-quarter%20earnings%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3EZuckerberg%20gloated%20about%20Meta%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20its%20AI%20assistant%20rolled%20out%20earlier%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20being%20%26quot%3Bon%20track%20to%20achieve%20our%20goal%20of%20becoming%20the%20most%20used%20AI%20assistant%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20good%20reason%20Zuckerberg%20is%20sounding%20so%20confident%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20reported%20having%203.27%20billion%20daily%20active%20users%20across%20all%20of%20its%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20Facebook%20Messenger%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Threads%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20user%20base%20that%20no%20one%20else%20can%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20user%20base%20that%20has%20remained%20close%20to%20Meta's%20family%20of%20apps%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20company's%20daily%20active%20users%20grew%207%25%20year-on-year%20in%20June%2C%20while%20Facebook%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Instagram%20users%20continue%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oberlo.com%2Fstatistics%2Faverage-time-spent-on-social-media%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esink%20more%20than%2016%20hours%20of%20screentime%20into%20the%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20effect%2C%20then%2C%20that%20gives%20Zuckerberg%20a%20lot%20of%20engaged%20users%20to%20introduce%20AI-powered%20technology%20to.%20But%20instead%20of%20giving%20users%20a%20choice%2C%20Meta%20is%20implementing%20a%20strategy%20that%20provides%20users%20with%20no%20option%20to%20opt-out%20of%20using%20its%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20puts%20it%20in%20a%20unique%20place%20to%20roll%20out%20new%20AI%20features%2C%20the%20same%20way%20it%20rolled%20out%20the%20Facebook%20Wall%20in%202004%20and%20had%20users%20adopt%20it.%20In%20contrast%2C%20users%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt5-gpt4-expectations-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompetitors%20like%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Anthropic%20have%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20product%20and%20seek%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20hasn't%20been%20lost%20on%20analysts.%20After%20earnings%2C%20Mike%20Proulx%2C%20vice%20president%20and%20research%20director%20at%20Forrester%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20smart%20move%20by%20the%20company%20to%2C%20effectively%2C%20introduce%20Meta%20AI%20to%20its%20users%20by%20forcing%20them%20to%20use%20it.%26quot