The%20man%2C%20portrayed%20by%20Park%20Jung-min%2C%20initially%20encounters%20a%20zombie%20outbreak%20during%20his%20mandatory%20military%20service.%20His%20girlfriend%2C%20played%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Patrick%20Frater%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fblackpink-jisoo-korea-zombie-series-newtopia-1236092425%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fblackpink-jisoo-korea-zombie-series-newtopia-1236092425%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fblackpink-jisoo-korea-zombie-series-newtopia-1236092425%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Is%20Sam%20Altman%20Wrong%20About%20India's%20AI%20Capabilities%3F%20Yes%2C%20And%20No%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F80dn6rf8_sam-altman_625x300_01_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%207%20last%20year%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20was%20asked%20this%20question%20when%20he%20was%20in%20India%3A%20Can%20Indian%20entrepreneurs%20compete%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20or%20should%20they%20even%20try%3F%20His%20answer%2C%20a%20blunt%20and%20definitive%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20jarring%20to%20most%20of%20us.%20%C2%A0Altman%20followed%20with%20an%20even%20more%20fundamental%20question%20of%20his%20own%3A%20was%20India%20even%20a%20player%20in%20this%20massive%20technological%20shift.%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Altman%20may%20have%20a%20point%2C%20he%20is%20wrong%20in%20assessing%20the%20depth%20of%20talent%20that%20India%20has%20and%20the%20potential%20it%20holds%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20AI%20revolution.%20India%20is%20a%20country%20with%20more%20than%205%2C000%20years%20of%20sustained%20human%20history%2C%20which%20has%20witnessed%20massive%20wars%2C%20famines%2C%20occupations%20and%20diversity.%20It%20holds%20the%20civilisational%20knowledge%20and%20accumulated%20thought%20processes%20that%20can%20and%20will%20play%20a%20critical%20part%20in%20building%20a%20safe%20and%20sustainable%20future%20for%20a%20man-machine%20society.%20India%20can%20act%20as%20a%20crucial%20counterbalance%20to%20an%20AI%20framework%20developed%20in%20the%20echo%20chambers%20of%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESilicon%20Valley's%20Flawed%20AI%20Playbook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20typical%20Silicon%20Valley%20fashion%20of%20moving%20fast%20and%20breaking%20things%2C%20OpenAI%20has%20chosen%20to%20open%20up%20the%20AI%20revolution%20to%20everyone.%20ChatGPT%20was%20developed%20by%20training%20AI%20on%20the%20vast%20and%20free%20human%20knowledge%20available%20on%20the%20internet.%20We%20have%20Elon%20Musk%20unleashing%20his%20bots%20developed%20on%20Twitter%20data%2C%20and%20humanoids%20on%20the%20shop%20floors%20of%20Tesla.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20is%20unloading%20billions%20on%20AI%20development%20and%20computing%2C%20while%20releasing%20large%20open-source%20models.%20Amazon%20is%20buying%20power%20utilities%20in%20gigawatts%20as%20the%20Artificial%20General%20Intelligence%20(AGI)%20race%20gets%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GPU-guzzling%2C%20greed-driven%20AI%20boom%20is%20already%20scary%2C%20and%20adding%20fuel%20to%20this%20are%20the%20geopolitical%20dynamics%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China.%20The%20world%20is%20set%20to%20witness%20an%20unprecedented%20%26quot%3BIntelligence%20explosion%26quot%3B.%20And%20we%20as%20a%20society%20probably%20aren't%20ready%20for%20such%20a%20rapid%20transition%20shaped%20purely%20by%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20playbook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersonal%20Stake%20In%20AI's%20Future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20parent%20of%20two%20young%20kids%2C%20I%20think%20selfishly.%20While%20I%20have%20been%20dabbling%20with%20AI%20for%20more%20than%2015%20years%2C%20I%20want%20my%20kids%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20a%20world%20that%20is%20truly%20open%20to%20exploring%20human%20potential.%20It%20was%20a%20rainy%20afternoon%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%202008%20when%20I%20came%20across%20an%20article%20by%20Ray%20Curzweil%2C%20which%20said%20that%20the%20sum%20total%20of%20all%20AI%20would%20be%20more%20than%20human%20intelligence%20by%202029.%20The%20claim%20shook%20me%3B%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20game-changing%20moment%20for%20humanity%2C%20primarily%20because%20we%20are%20unsure%20of%20what%20lies%20beyond%20that%20point%20-%20a%20'Singularity'%20-%20and%20the%20shape%20society%20would%20take%20after%20that.%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20made%20the%20crazy%20decision%20to%20resign%20from%20my%20well-paying%20job%20at%20Wipro%20to%20start%20India's%20first%20AI%20chatbot%20company%2C%20'Vimagino'%2C%20with%20three%20friends%20and%20fellow%20IIT%20Kanpur%20alumni.%20Some%20remnants%20of%20this%20chatbot%20demo%20can%20still%20be%20found%20on%20YouTube.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMind%20you%2C%20this%20was%20two%20years%20before%20OpenAI%20was%20born%20(even%20before%20the%20pre-deep-learning%20era)%2C%20and%20it%20was%20all%20done%20in%20India.%20We%20even%20went%20live%20on%20two%20websites%2C%20Indiatimeshopping.com%20and%20Yatra.com.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20couldn't%20grow%20because%20not%20many%20back%20then%20practised%20risk-funding%20that%20could%20back%20such%20companies%20in%20India.%20Perhaps%20we%20were%20a%20little%20too%20early%20(or%20were%20we).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20eventually%20ended%20up%20co-founding%20pi%20Ventures%2C%20an%20early-stage%20venture%20fund%2C%20with%20Manish%20Singhal.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20back%20risky%20AI%20bets%20in%20India%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20tracking%20well%20today%20and%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20becoming%20a%20revenue-making%20AI%20unicorn%20-%20a%20rarity%20in%20this%20GenAI%20era.%20However%2C%20I%20can%20see%20that%20while%20these%20AI%20companies%20from%20India%20could%20do%20well%2C%20eventually%2C%20for-profit%20companies%20would%20have%20to%20optimise%20functions%20like%20revenue%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20profit.%20It%20rankled%20me%20that%20if%20for-profit%20businesses%20made%20their%20way%20to%20AGI%2C%20the%20pursuit%20of%20profit%20might%20lead%20to%20AI%20ignoring%20humanity.%20We%20could%20end%20up%20being%20just%20dressed-up%20animals%20in%20a%20cage%2C%20well-fed%20with%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%2C%20but%2C%20in%20all%20actuality%2C%20complete%20non-players%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things.%20That%20is%20a%20very%20depressing%20scenario.%20So%2C%20I%20stepped%20back%20from%20pi%20and%20helped%20co-found%20ARTPARK%20(AI%20%26amp%3B%20Robotics%20Technology%20Park)%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20organisation%20whose%20motto%20is%20to%20make%20AI%20work%20for%20humanity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELanguages%2C%20'%3Cem%3EShruti%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20And%20'%3Cem%3ESmruti%3C%2Fem%3E'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EARTPAR%2C%20supported%20by%20a%20Rs%20230%20crore%20seed%20grant%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20and%20the%20government%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20is%20a%20unique%20effort%20incubated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc).%20The%20organisation%20recently%20released%2016%2C000%20hours%20of%20spontaneous%20speech%20from%2080%20districts%20under%20project%20Vaani%2C%20open-sourced%20under%20Bhashini.%20Such%20initiatives%20can%20help%20in%20the%20development%20of%20geographically%20anchored%20models%20in%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20which%20is%20packed%20with%20diverse%20languages%20and%20local%20dialects%20that%20sometimes%20change%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20few%20kilometres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20languages%20are%20rivers%20of%20knowledge%2C%20overflowing%20with%20rich%20human%20intelligence%20and%20enriched%20by%20centuries%20of%20usage%2C%20feedback%2C%20and%20historical%20chronicling%20of%20local%20events.%20This%20longitudinal%20data%20of%20human%20effort%20spanning%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20trying%20to%20describe%20the%20world%20around%2C%20is%20a%20living%2C%20thriving%20body%20of%20human%2C%20annotated%20knowledge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20unique%20thing%20about%20India%3A%20a%20lot%20of%20its%20collective%20knowledge%20exists%20in%20%26quot%3Bshruti%26quot%3B(in%20voice)%20and%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Bsmruti%26quot%3B(in%20memory)%20as%20centuries%20of%20invaders%20destroyed%20its%20written%20knowledge%20and%20manuscripts.%20This%20method%20even%20allowed%20the%20Upanishads%20to%20survive%20over%20time.%20For%20centuries%2C%20this%20knowledge%20has%20been%20practised%20as%20living%20traditions%2C%20weaved%20into%20the%20daily%20lives%20of%20billions.%20The%20physicist%20Ervin%20Schr%C3%B6dinger%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20reality%20and%20is%20known%20for%20his%20Schr%C3%B6dinger's%20cat%20experiment%2C%20reportedly%20carried%20a%20translation%20of%20the%20Upanishads%20and%20revered%20its%20core%20insights%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20apparent%20duality.%20Indeed%2C%20its%20unique%20views%20on%20self-knowledge%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20reality%20and%20consciousness%20can%20help%20chart%20a%20new%20way%20of%20thinking%20about%20safe%20AI%20as%20we%20race%20towards%20the%20so-called%20'AGI'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%203%20Stages%20Of%20AI%20Development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20stages%20that%20mark%20the%20learning%20and%20development%20of%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStage%201%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20learning%20from%20freely%20available%20data%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20such%20systems%20powered%20by%20LLMs.%20It%20has%20become%20useful%20in%20creating%20text%20and%20solving%20other%20problems%2C%20though%20it's%20still%20not%20alarmingly%20influential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStage%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20about%20creating%20AI%20agents%2C%20that%20research%2C%20co-work%20with%20and%20co-learn%20from%20human%20feedback.%20It's%20here%20that%20India%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%201.4%20billion%20brought%20up%20on%20a%20rich%20diversity%20of%20thought%20and%20action%2C%20can%20play%20a%20big%20role.%20We%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20to%20some%20aspects%20of%20AGI%20at%20this%20stage.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStage%203%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20all%20about%20learning%20and%20augmenting%20from%20the%20physical%20and%20digital%20world.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20be%20tricky%20and%20critical%2C%20and%20we%20will%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20what%20AI%20ends%20up%20learning%2C%20because%20it%20will%20soon%20power%2040-50%25%20of%20the%20workflow%20in%20real-life%20situations.%20It's%20this%20stage%20that%20will%20truly%20power%20a%20man-machine%20society%20of%207.5%20billion%20humans%20working%20with%20more%20than%2030%20billion%20intelligent%20machines.%20%C2%A0Unlike%20human%20beings%2C%20biases%20in%20AI%20technology%20can%20grow%20exponentially%2C%20and%20in%20a%20much%20shorter%20span%20of%20time%2C%20humbling%20creators%20if%20they%20are%20not%20careful.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Must%20Take%20The%20Lead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20with%20its%20powerful%20internet%20and%20social%20media%20giants%20driven%20by%20profits%2C%20may%20end%20up%20creating%20a%20path%20to%20AI%20that%20puts%20profit%20ahead%20of%20humanity.%20China%2C%20which%20is%20prone%20to%20imprinting%20its%20central%20leader's%20thinking%20onto%20algorithms%20to%20exact%20control%2C%20may%20power%20a%20future%20where%20AI%20might%20rule%20over%20human%20beings.%20Both%20scenarios%20are%20not%20sustainable.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20India%2C%20with%20its%20rich%2C%20sustainable%2C%20civilisational%20history%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20shape%20a%20future%20where%20humans%20can%20realise%20their%20full%20potential%2C%20together%20with%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman%20might%20have%20been%20wrong%20about%20India's%20potential%20contribution%2C%20but%20he%20was%20spot-on%20about%20the%20inadequate%20resources%20we%20are%20putting%20into%20becoming%20an%20AI%20force%20to%20reckon%20with%20at%20a%20global%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20AI%20mission%20is%20a%20great%20start%2C%20but%20we%20need%20to%20double%20down%20with%20a%20sizable%20private%20capital%20pool%20and%20AI%20compute%20resources%20that%20can%20support%20our%20talented%20technologists%20and%20researchers.%20We%20need%20to%20enable%20them%20at%20warp%20speed%20to%20digitize%20and%20mine%20the%20rich%20civilizational%20knowledge%20India%20possesses%20for%20building%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20our%20kids%20may%20not%20like%20the%20'Matrix'%20future%20we%20may%20leave%20for%20them.%20Maybe%20it's%20time%20for%20India%20to%20take%20the%20'Red%20Pill'%20and%20pull%20up%20its%20socks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BUmakant%20Soni%20is%20chairman%20of%20AIfoundry%2C%20co-founder%20of%20ARTPARK%20(AI%20%26amp%3B%20Robotics%20Technology%20Park)%2C%20and%20a%20passionate%20advocate%20for%20inclusive%20development%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722504540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmbceuguo_sam-altman_625x300_01_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-sam-altman-wrong-about-indias-ai-capabilities-yes-and-no-6238818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20June%207%20last%20year%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20was%20asked%20this%20question%20when%20he%20was%20in%20India%3A%20Can%20Indian%20entrepreneurs%20compete%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20or%20should%20they%20even%20try%3F%20His%20answer%20was%20a%20blunt%20and%20definitive%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-sam-altman-wrong-about-indias-ai-capabilities-yes-and-no-6238818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-sam-altman-wrong-about-indias-ai-capabilities-yes-and-no-6238818%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-sam-altman-wrong-about-indias-ai-capabilities-yes-and-no-6238818%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Navi%20Mumbai%20Murder%20Accused%20Scaled%20A%20New%20Mountain%20Every%20Day%20To%20Escape%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20the%20body%20of%2020-year-old%20Yashashree%20Shinde%20was%20found%20carrying%20multiple%20stab%20wounds%20and%20dumped%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai's%20Uran%20area.%20After%20a%205-day%20hunt%20for%20the%20killer%2C%20police%20arrested%20Dawood%20Shaikh%2C%20whose%20advances%20were%20rejected%20by%20Yashashree%2C%20from%20Karnataka's%20Gulbarga%20district.%20As%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20murder%20delves%20deeper%2C%20chilling%20details%20have%20emerged%20about%20how%20Dawood%20planned%20the%20murder%20and%20evaded%20police%20for%20nearly%20a%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Backdrop%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20origins%20of%20this%20crime%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%202019%20when%20a%20POCSO%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Dawood%20Shaikh%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Yashashree's%20father.%20Dawood%20was%20arrested%20and%20spent%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20in%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDawood%2C%20harbouring%20feelings%20for%20Yashashree%2C%20wanted%20to%20marry%20her%20and%20relocate%20to%20Karnataka.%20However%2C%20Yashashree%20refused%20his%20advances%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20persistent%20pressure%20campaign%20from%20Dawood.%20Whenever%20Yashashree%20blocked%20his%20number%2C%20Dawood%20would%20use%20his%20friend%20Mohsin's%20phone%20to%20continue%20communicating%20with%20her.%20His%20obsession%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20he%20began%20threatening%20her%20with%20private%20photographs%2C%20blackmailing%20her%20into%20meeting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2022%2C%20Dawood%20left%20Karnataka%20and%20arrived%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%20on%20the%2023rd.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20he%20pressed%20Yashashree%20to%20meet%20him%2C%20which%20she%20initially%20refused.%20On%20July%2025%2C%20in%20a%20desperate%20move%2C%20Dawood%20posted%20one%20of%20the%20private%20photos%20on%20Facebook%2C%20coercing%20Yashashree%20into%20meeting%20him%20to%20ensure%20the%20photo%20was%20deleted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20murder%2C%20Yashashree%2C%20who%20had%20taken%20a%20half-day%20leave%20from%20her%20job%20in%20Belapur%2C%20met%20Dawood%20near%20Jui%20Nagar%20railway%20station.%20A%20heated%20argument%20ensued%2C%20during%20which%20Dawood%20killed%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYashashree's%20body%20was%20found%20on%20Saturday%2C%20dumped%20in%20the%20bushes%20near%20a%20railway%20station%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai's%20Uran%20area%20with%20multiple%20stab%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20Dawood%20had%20brought%20two%20knives%20from%20Bangalore.%20On%20July%2025%2C%20during%20their%20meeting%2C%20the%20situation%20escalated%2C%20and%20Dawood%20killed%20Yashashree%20with%20one%20of%20the%20knives.%20Panicked%20and%20desperate%20to%20flee%2C%20he%20made%20his%20way%20from%20Uran%20to%20Panvel%20by%20train%2C%20withdrew%20money%20from%20an%20ATM%2C%20and%20then%20took%20a%20bus%20to%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20tattoos%20bearing%20Dawood's%20name%20were%20found%20on%20Yashashree's%20body.%20Whether%20Yashashree%20willingly%20got%20her%20body%20tattooed%20or%20was%20forced%20to%20do%20so%20by%20Dawood%20is%20being%20investigated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Manhunt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAware%20that%20his%20mobile%20phone%20could%20lead%20the%20police%20to%20him%2C%20Dawood%20turned%20it%20off%20and%20left%20it%20with%20his%20grandmother%20in%20Karnataka.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20began%20a%20journey%20on%20foot%2C%20traversing%20the%20mountains%20near%20his%20village%20to%20evade%20capture.%20Dawood's%20plan%20was%20to%20climb%20one%20mountain%2C%20descend%2C%20and%20then%20move%20on%20to%20the%20next%2C%20continuously%20moving%20to%20avoid%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20before%20the%20murder%2C%20on%20July%2020%2C%20a%20Panvel%20court%20issued%20a%20Non-Bailable%20Warrant%20(NBW)%20against%20Dawood%20for%20his%20failure%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20regarding%20the%202019%20POCSO%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navi%20Mumbai%20police%2C%20piecing%20together%20Dawood's%20movements%2C%20launched%20a%20massive%20manhunt.%20Using%20human%20intelligence%2C%20they%20tracked%20him%20down%20to%20a%20mountain%20near%20Shahpur%20in%20Karnataka.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2030%2C%20after%20five%20days%20of%20relentless%20pursuit%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%20Dawood%20from%20the%20mountains%20at%20around%205%20AM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722504420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fggqqm57o_navi-mumbai-murder_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdawood-shaikh-yashashree-shinde-inside-navi-mumbai-murder-accused-hid-in-mountains-after-killing-woman-6238700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Saturday%2C%20the%20body%20of%2020-year-old%20Yashashree%20Shinde%20was%20found%20carrying%20multiple%20stab%20wounds%20and%20dumped%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai's%20Uran%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagem