o%20heard%20Hindu%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20arguments%20concluded%20and%20the%20court%20reserved%20its%20order%20the%20application%20was%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20management%20committee%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20with%20the%20prayers%20to%20%26quot%3Bissue%20appropriate%20directions%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20right%20of%20an%20audience%20through%20video%20conferencing...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20the%20counsel%20had%20been%20present%20through%20video%20conferencing%20on%20several%20occasions%20and%20in%20person%20before%20the%20court.%20He%20had%20ample%20opportunity%20to%20argue%20the%20matter%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20principle%20of%20transparency%2C%20the%20court%20accepted%20the%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Intezamia%20Committee%20had%20challenged%20maintainability%20of%20the%20petitions%2C%20including%20one%20filed%20by%20Bhagwan%20Shrikrishna%20Virajman%20at%20the%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20temple%2C%20which%20claims%20the%20mosque%20is%20built%20on%2013.37%20acres%20of%20land%20that%20belongs%20to%20the%20temple%20and%20sought%20its%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20side%20claims%20the%20land%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20Lord%20Krishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20claim%20as%20evidence%20some%20lotus%20carvings%20on%20the%20mosque%2C%20as%20well%20as%20shapes%20supposedly%20resembling%20the%20'%3Cem%3Esheshnag%3C%2Fem%3E'%20or%20the%20snake%20demigod%20in%20Hindu%20mythology.%20These%20are%20proof%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20built%20over%20a%20temple%2C%20they%20argue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20side%20had%20earlier%20sought%20to%20dismiss%20these%20petitions%20by%20citing%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20of%201991%2C%20which%20maintains%20the%20religious%20status%20of%20any%20place%20as%20it%20was%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20an%20agreement%20