ces-too-high-fast-food-restaurant-falling-sales-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOffering%20value%20is%20going%20to%20be%20key%20to%20winning%20customers%20back%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20been%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20on%20the%20struggles%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-price-hikes-putting-off-low-income-customers-inflation-expensive-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elower-income%20customers%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20it%20said%20that%20these%20diners%20were%20placing%20smaller%20orders%20and%20opting%20to%20eat%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-fast-food-is-so-much-more-expensive-value-affordable-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20is%20fatigued%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20rising%20restaurant%20prices%2C%20Jim%20Sanderson%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Northcoast%20Research%2C%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-is-expensive-people-annoyed-eating-out-restaurant-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloyal%20fast%20food%20fans%3C%2Fa%3E%20say%20they're%20switching%20up%20their%20routine%20and%20becoming%20less%20tolerant%20of%20the%20price%20increases%20as%20grocery%20prices%20fall%20and%20the%20value%20proposition%20of%20fast%20food%20becomes%20less%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-promises-more-value-menu-deals-to-win-back-customers-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722501031000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66aa57de1a227600e6331687%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-promises-more-value-menu-deals-to-win-back-customers-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McDonald's%20CEO%20discussed%20its%20%245%20value%20meal%20and%20its%20plans%20to%20address%20the%20chain's%20value%20problem%20amid%20rising%20prices%20and%20customer%20dissatisfaction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mary%20Hanbury)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A81%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-promises-more-value-menu-deals-to-win-back-customers-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20People%20In%20This%20Indian%20Hill%20Paradise%20Need%20Not%20Pay%20Income%20Tax%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20scrambled%20to%20meet%20the%20July%2031%20deadline%20for%20filing%20Income%20Tax%20Returns%20(ITR)%2C%20one%20state%20remained%20blissfully%20exempt%20from%20the%20tax%20frenzy%20-%20Sikkim.%20Thanks%20to%20a%20special%20provision%20under%20Section%2010%20(26AAA)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%20Sikkim%20has%20been%20spared%20from%20paying%20income%20tax%20since%20its%20merger%20with%20India.%20This%20exemption%20was%20granted%20to%20preserve%20the%20state's%20existing%20tax%20structure%2C%20which%20was%20in%20place%20before%20it%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20its%20accession%20to%20India%2C%20Sikkim%20had%20its%20own%20tax%20system%2C%20and%20its%20residents%20were%20not%20subject%20to%20the%20Indian%20Income%20Tax%20Act.%20The%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20to%20maintain%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20granted%20Sikkim%20special%20exemptions%20from%20income%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESikkim%20Income%20Tax%20Exemption%20Act%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Budget%20of%202008%20repealed%20the%20Sikkim%20Tax%20Act%20and%20exempted%20Sikkim%20residents%20from%20paying%20income%20tax%20through%20Section%2010(26AAA)%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act.%20This%20move%20was%20made%20to%20preserve%20Sikkim's%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20371(f)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20Association%20of%20Old%20Settlers%20of%20Sikkim%20and%20others%20challenged%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ey.com%2Fen_in%2Falerts-hub%2F2023%2F04%2Fsupreme-court-expands-scope-of-tax-exemption-for-sikkimese-individuals%5C%22%3ESection%2010(26AAA)%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Income-tax%20Act%2C%201961%2C%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20They%20argued%20that%20the%20definition%20of%20%26quot%3BSikkimese%26quot%3B%20under%20this%20section%20unfairly%20excluded%20two%20categories%20of%20individuals%20from%20tax%20exemption%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndians%20settled%20in%20Sikkim%20before%20it%20merged%20with%20India%20on%20April%2026%2C%201975.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESikkimese%20women%20who%20married%20non-Sikkimese%20men%20after%20April%201%2C%202008.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Section%2010(26AAA)%2C%20introduced%20by%20the%20Finance%20Act%20of%202008%20(effective%20retroactively%20from%20the%20tax%20year%201989-90)%2C%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BSikkimese%26quot%3B%20included%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndividuals%20listed%20in%20the%20Sikkim%20Subjects%20Register%20before%20April%2026%2C%201975.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndividuals%20added%20to%20the%20register%20by%20government%20orders%20in%201990%20and%201991.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndividuals%20whose%20close%20relatives%20(father%2C%20husband%2C%20paternal%20grandfather%20or%20brother)%20are%20listed%20in%20the%20register.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20definition%20covered%20most%20of%20Sikkim's%20population%20but%20excluded%20around%201%20per%20cent%20-%20Indians%20who%20settled%20in%20Sikkim%20before%20April%2026%2C%201975%2C%20and%20chose%20not%20to%20give%20up%20their%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%20so%20their%20names%20were%20not%20in%20the%20Sikkim%20Subjects%20Register.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taxpayers%20argued%20this%20exclusion%20was%20unfair%20and%20discriminatory.%20They%20wanted%20the%20tax%20exemption%20to%20include%20all%20individuals%20settled%20in%20Sikkim%20before%20April%201%2C%201975%2C%20whose%20names%20were%20not%20in%20the%20register.%20They%20also%20argued%20that%20denying%20the%20exemption%20to%20Sikkimese%20women%20marrying%20non-Sikkimese%20men%20after%20April%201%2C%202008%2C%20was%20discriminatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court%20ruling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20it%20was%20indeed%20discriminatory%20to%20deny%20tax%20exemptions%20to%20Sikkimese%20women%20married%20to%20non-Sikkimese%20men%20after%20April%201%2C%202008.%20This%20rule%20did%20not%20apply%20to%20Sikkimese%20men%20who%20married%20non-Sikkimese%20women%20or%20to%20Sikkimese%20women%20who%20married%20non-Sikkimese%20men%20before%20this%20date.%20The%20Court%20found%20this%20rule%20unfair%20and%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20equality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Indians%20settled%20in%20Sikkim%20before%20April%2026%2C%201975%2C%20whose%20names%20are%20not%20in%20the%20Sikkim%20Subjects%20Register%2C%20the%20judges%20agreed%20that%20the%20denial%20of%20exemption%20was%20discriminatory%20but%20suggested%20different%20solutions.%20Justice%20MR%20Shah%20struck%20down%20the%20rule%20denying%20the%20exemption%2C%20while%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20used%20Article%20142%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20direct%20the%20Centre%20to%20add%20a%20clause%20to%20Section%2010(26AAA)%20to%20grant%20tax%20exemptions%20to%20these%20individuals.%20Until%20the%20law%20is%20amended%2C%20she%20ordered%20that%20these%20individuals%20should%20still%20get%20the%20tax%20exemption%20under%20Section%2010(26AAA).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722501000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F4fnl6cvg_sikkim-generic_625x300_10_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-people-in-this-indian-hill-paradise-need-not-pay-income-tax-6237083%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20scrambled%20to%20meet%20the%20July%2031%20deadline%20for%20filing%20Income%20Tax%20Returns%20(ITR)%2C%20one%20state%20remained%20blissfully%20exempt%20from%20the%20tax%20frenzy%20-%20Sikkim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-people-in-this-indian-hill-paradise-need-not-pay-income-tax-6237083%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Festival%20Favorite%20Film%20%E2%80%98The%20Cloud%20and%20the%20Man%E2%80%99%20Gets%20U.S.%20Release%20From%20Outsider%20Pictures%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722500952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FThe-Cloud-and-the-Man1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236092364%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Outsider%20Pictures%20is%20bringing%20the%20critically%20acclaimed%20Indian%20Bengali-language%20film%20%E2%80%9CManikbabur%20Megh%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%9CThe%20Cloud%20and%20the%20Man%E2%80%9D)%20to%20U.S.%20shores%20on%20Aug.%209.%20The%20film%2C%20which%20has%20been%20making%20waves%20in%20Bengal%20since%20its%20July%2012%20theatrical%20release%2C%20will%20initially%20open%20in%20Chicago%20and%20San%20Jose.%20Directed%20by%20newcomer%20Abhinandan%20Banerjee%2C%20the%20film%20tells%20the%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fthe-cloud-and-the-man-us-release-outsider-pictures-1236092364%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fthe-cloud-and-the-man-us-release-outsider-pictures-1236092364%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fthe-cloud-and-the-man-us-release-outsider-pictures-1236092364%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shooter%20Swapnil%20wins%20bronze%2C%20India's%203rd%20medal%20of%20Paris%20Olympics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722500859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112191979%2Cimgsize-38066.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fparis-olympics-2024%2Findiaparis%2Fshooter-swapnil-kusale-wins-bronze-indias-third-medal-of-paris-olympics%2Farticleshow%2F112191053.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20shooting%20contingent%20continued%20to%20fire%20medals%20on%20day%20six%20of%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20with%20Swapnil%20Kusale%20winning%20a%20bronze%20medal%20in%20men's%2050m%20Rifle%203%20Positions%20event%20with%20a%20score%20of%20451.4.%20It's%20the%20third%20medal%20of%20the%20Paris%20Games%20for%20India%20and%20third%20bronze.%20It's%20the%20first%20time%20that%20India%20have%20won%20three%20shooting%20medals%20at%20a%20single%20edition%20of%20the%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20tense%20after%20clashes%20erupt%2C%20security%20forces%20fire%20tear%20gas%20shells%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722500630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112191501%2Cimgsize-27598.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmanipur-clashes-erupt-after-security-forces-fire-tear-gas-shells-to-disperse-crowd%2Farticleshow%2F112191034.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Manipur's%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20tensions%20flared%20between%20Internally%20Displaced%20Persons%20(IDPs)%20and%20security%20forces.%20Tear%20gas%20was%20used%20to%20disperse%20protestors%20demanding%20rehabilitation%20and%20an%20end%20to%20ethnic%20violence.%20Around%20100%20IDPs%20were%20involved%2C%20with%20additional%20confrontations%20occurring.%20The%20conflict%2C%20which%20began%20in%20May%202023%2C%20has%20claimed%20226%20lives%20and%20displaced%20over%2059%2C000%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Satellite%20Images%20Show%20Devastation%20From%20Landslides%20In%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHigh%20resolution%20images%20taken%20by%20Indian%20satellites%20show%20the%20widespread%20damage%20and%20devastation%20caused%20by%20landslides%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%20More%20than%20150%20people%20have%20died%20and%20over%20200%20injured%20even%20as%20the%20rescue%20works%20are%20ongoing.%20The%20before%20and%20after%20images%20show%20that%20about%2086%2C000%20square%20meters%20of%20land%20slipped%20and%20the%20debris%20flowed%20for%20about%208%20kilometers%20along%20the%20Iruvaiphuzha%20river.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20report%20also%20presents%20evidence%20of%20an%20old%20landslide%20at%20the%20same%20location%2C%20suggesting%20its%20vulnerability%20was%20documented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Center%2C%20Hyderabad%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organization%20deployed%20its%20highest%20resolution%20Cartosat-3%20optical%20satellite%20and%20the%20RISAT%20satellite%20that%20is%20capable%20of%20seeing%20through%20cloud%20cover.%20The%20space%20agency%20says%20the%20landslide%20was%20initiated%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%201550%20meters%20above%20the%20sea%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20report%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%2C%20suggests%20that%20there%20is%20evidence%20of%20an%20old%20landslide%20at%20the%20same%20location.%20A%202023%20'Landslide%20Atlas%20of%20India'%20prepared%20by%20ISRO%20had%20placed%20Wayanad%20region%20as%20a%20vulnerable%20to%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F764in38_wayanad-satellite-images_625x300_01_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20NRSC%2FISRO%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20satellite%20images%20show%20widespread%20devastation%20at%20Wayanad%20landslide.%20Almost%2086%2C000%20square%20meters%20of%20land%20slipped%20causing%20the%20landslide%20almost%20five%20times%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan.%20The%20debris%20flowed%20for%20almost%208%20kilometers%20downstream%20washing%20away%20towns%20and%20settlements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20says%20there%20is%20evidence%20of%20an%20old%20landslide%20at%20same%20location.%20The%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Center%20used%20the%20Cartosat-3%20satellite%20and%20the%20RISAT%20satellite%20to%20see%20through%20cloud%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NRSC%20reports%20says%20%26quot%3Ba%20major%20debris%20flow%20was%20triggered%20by%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Chooralmala%20town%20of%20Wayanad%20District%20in%20Kerala%20state%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVery%20high%20resolution%20RISAT%20SAR%20images%20of%2031%20July%2C%202024%20show%20the%20entire%20extent%20of%20the%20debris%20flow%20from%20crown%20to%20end%20of%20run%20out%20zone.%20The%20approximate%20length%20of%20the%20flow%20is%208%20km.%20The%20crown%20zone%20is%20a%20reactivation%20of%20an%20older%20landslide.%20The%20size%20of%20the%20main%20scarp%20of%20the%20landslide%20in%2086%2C000%20square%20meters.%20The%20debris%20flow%20has%20widened%20the%20course%20of%20the%20Iruvaniphuza%20River%20causing%20breach%20of%20its%20banks.%20Houses%20and%20other%20infrastructures%20located%20along%20the%20banks%20have%20been%20damaged%20by%20the%20debris%20flow%2C%203D%20rendition%20of%20the%20crown%20of%20the%20landslide%20illustrates%20that%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20hill%20slope%20has%20been%20affected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F9i31l85g_wayanad-satellite-images_625x300_01_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20NRSC%2FISRO%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20areal%20extent%20of%20the%20landslide%20is%2086%2C000%20square%20meters.%20The%20crown%20is%20located%20at%20an%20approximate%20elevation%20of%20approximately%201%2C550%20m%20above%20MSL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20prepared%20a%20%26quot%3BLandslide%20Atlas%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20which%20diligently%20documents%20the%2080%2C000%20landslides%20that%20have%20occurred%20over%2020%20years%20and%20lists%20landslide%20from%20Puthumala%2C%20Wayanad%20district%2C%20and%20large%20parts%20of%20Kerala%20are%20marked%20red%20as%20being%20prone%20to%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20S%20Somanath%2C%20the%20Chairman%20of%20ISRO%20in%20the%202023%20report%20says%20it%20presents%20%26quot%3Bthe%20overall%20landslide%20scenario%20in%20India%20and%20...%20the%20field%20of%20landslide%20hazard.%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20the%20atlas%20will%20be%20beneficial%20to%20everyone%20involved%20in%20disaster%20management%20endeavors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722500460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F0evh977g_wayanad-satellite-images_625x300_01_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-landslide-isro-satellite-images-find-evidence-of-old-landslide-at-same