isons%2C%20execution%20sites%2C%20and%20crime%20scenes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDark%20tourism%20destinations%20may%20include%20the%20Chernobyl%20exclusion%20zone%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20Killing%20Fields%20in%20Cambodia%2C%20the%20Auschwitz%20camp%20in%20Poland%2C%20and%20the%209%2F11%20Memorial%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20sites%20might%20be%20haunted%20houses%2C%20paranormal%20activity%2C%20or%20infamous%20historical%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefinitions%20of%20'dark%20tourism'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20earliest%20definitions%20of%20dark%20tourism%20was%20provided%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2F0826450644%2Fref%3Das_li_qf_asin_il_tl%3Fie%3DUTF8%26tag%3Dlifeasabutter-21%26creative%3D6738%26linkCode%3Das2%26creativeASIN%3D0826450644%26linkId%3Dea7f09c74fbeea0c9125d950ed1088ff%C2%A0%5C%22%3EJohn%20Lennon%20and%20Malcolm%20Foley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20representation%20of%20inhuman%20acts%2C%20and%20how%20these%20are%20interpreted%20for%20visitors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20more%20recent%20definition%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1002%2F9781405165518.wbeosd045.pub2%5C%22%3EKevin%20Fox%20Gotham%3C%2Fa%3E%20expands%20on%20this%20idea%2C%20describing%20dark%20tourism%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20circulation%20of%20people%20to%20places%20characterised%20by%20distress%2C%20atrocity%20or%20sadness%20and%20pain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gotham%20also%20introduced%20the%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3Bdisaster%20tourism%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20refers%20to%20situations%20where%20tourism%20rises%20in%20response%20to%20a%20major%20disaster%20or%20traumatic%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20dark%20tourism%20is%20popular%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20dark%20tourism%20lies%20in%20the%20emotional%20connection%20they%20make%20with%20a%20place%20of%20tragedy.%20Visitors%20seek%20to%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20the%20history%20and%20culture%20of%20a%20location%20and%20connect%20with%20the%20emotions%20of%20those%20who%20experienced%20the%20tragedy%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20visiting%20these%20sites%2C%20people%20can%20tangibly%20engage%20with%20the%20past%2C%20paying%20respects%20to%20those%20who%20suffered.%20Dark%20tourism%20allows%20individuals%20to%20process%20and%20understand%20the%20significance%20of%20historical%20events%20and%20reflect%20on%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722500100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-09%2Fauschwitz-memorial650_650x400_81441163783.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkerala-police-has-warned-against-dark-tourism-know-what-it-is-6237006%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dark%20tourism%20has%20gained%20global%20attention%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20partly%20thanks%20to%20TV%20shows%20like%20Chernobyl%20and%20The%20Dark%20Tourist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkerala-police-has-warned-against-dark-tourism-know-what-it-is-6237006%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkerala-police-has-warned-against-dark-tourism-know-what-it-is-6237006%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkerala-police-has-warned-against-dark-tourism-know-what-it-is-6237006%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICW%20outfit%20reminds%20Vicky%20of%20his%20wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722499841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112191289%2Cimgsize-37654.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-shine-at-icw-finale-says-outfits-reminded-me-of-my-wedding-felt-li