nd%20explain%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20consuming%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20experience%20of%20conducting%20such%20a%20campaign%2C%20Mahadevi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20would%20come%20home%20drunk%20and%20cause%20trouble%20for%20members%20in%20their%20homes.%20When%20young%20girls%20explained%20how%20their%20habit%20had%20been%20impacting%20the%20upbringing%20of%20their%20children%2C%20they%20were%20ashamed.%20But%20not%20everyone%20is%20as%20understanding%2C%20many%20people%20opposed%20us.%20However%2C%20we%20remained%20undeterred.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-4-1722331581.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20girls%20also%20take%20up%20initiatives%20such%20as%20organising%20cleanliness%20drives%20in%20the%20village.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-4-1722331581.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-4-1722331581-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-4-1722331581-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-4-1722331581-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-4-1722331581-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359007%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20girls%20also%20take%20up%20initiatives%20such%20as%20organising%20cleanliness%20drives%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20at%20least%20300%20such%20girls%20in%20Nanded%20are%20taking%20leadership%20role