r-best-gram-panchayat-bengal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egram%20panchayats%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20Yerdi%2C%20Sawargaon%20Mal%2C%20and%20Amgavhan%20%E2%80%93%20for%20efficiently%20running%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahadevi%2C%20who%20now%20talks%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20society%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20feel%20that%20we%20lag%20behind%20anyone%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20where%20the%20president%2C%20finance%20minister%2C%20our%20sarpanch%2C%20and%20CEO%20are%20women.%20We%20do%20not%20feel%20any%20less.%20I%20aspire%20to%20become%20a%20sarpanch%20and%20lead%20my%20village%20one%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20Minal%20has%20recently%20launched%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20project%20in%20June.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20second%20leg%20of%20Balika%20Panchayat%20focuses%20on%20suggesting%20resolutions%20for%20gram%20panchayats.%20Our%20next%20goal%20is%20to%20see%20how%20these%20girls%20start%20giving%20resolutions%20with%20unanimity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20this%20initiative%20has%20been%20immensely%20satisfying%20for%20Minal.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20has%20been%20very%20fulfilling%20as%20it%20is%20apart%20from%20my%20routine%20work.%20If%20we%20could%20implement%20an%20idea%20on%20the%20grassroots%20where%20young%20rural%20girls%20feel%20confident%20and%20empowered%20in%20taking%20leadership%20roles%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20society%2C%20then%20we%20have%20already%20started%20achieving%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Minal%20Karanwal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722498878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-2_11zon-1722331557.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%