s%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court's%20Big%20Quota%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20seven-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20okayed%20sub-classification%20within%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20categories%20to%20provide%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%20for%20the%20more%20marginalised%20among%20backward%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landmark%20verdict%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20by%20a%206%3A1%20majority%2C%20with%20Justice%20Bela%20Trivedi%20dissenting.%20Six%20separate%20judgments%20were%20written.%20The%20verdict%20overrules%20the%202004%20judgment%20of%20a%20five-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20in%20the%20case%20of%20EV%20Chinnaiah%20vs%20State%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20other%20judges%20on%20the%20bench%20were%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20Justice%C2%A0Vikram%20Nath%2C%20Justice%20Pankaj%20Mithal%2C%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%20and%20Justice%20Satish%20Chandra%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20in%20favour%20of%20sub-classification%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20categories.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20had%20observed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20distinction%20between%20%26quot%3Bsub-classification%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsub-categorisation%26quot%3B%20and%20held%20that%20states%20may%20have%20to%20sub-categorise%20reserved%20category%20communities%20to%20ensure%20that%20benefits%20reach%20more%20backward%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20six%20opinions.%20mine%20is%20for%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%20and%20me.%20A%20majority%20of%20us%20has%20overruled%20EV%20Chinnaiah%20(verdict)%20and%20we%20hold%20sub-classification%20is%20permitted.%20Justice%20Bela%20trivedi%20has%20dissented%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20members%20of%20SC%2FST%20categories%20are%20not%20often%20unable%20to%20climb%20up%20the%20ladder%20due%20to%20the%20systemic%20discrimination%20they%20face.%20Article%2014%20permits%20sub-classification%20of%20caste%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BHistorical%20and%20empirical%20evidence%20demonstrates%20that%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20are%20a%20socially%20heterogenous%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20BR%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20referred%20to%20a%20speech%20of%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20in%201949%20where%20he%20said%20that%20unless%20we%20have%20social%20democracy%20there%20is%20no%20use%20of%20political%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHardships%20and%20backwardness%20suffered%20by%20some%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20is%20different%20for%20each%20caste.%20EV%20Chinnaiah%20was%20wrongly%20decided.%20It%20was%20argued%20that%20a%20party%20can%20give%20reservation%20to%20a%20sub-caste%20to%20gain%20political%20mileage%2C%20but%20I%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20this.%20The%20ultimate%20objective%20would%20be%20to%20realise%20real%20equality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDissenting%20with%20the%20majority%20judgment%2C%20Justice%20Trivedi%20said%20she%20does%20not%20approve%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20referred%20it%20to%20a%20larger%20bench%20without%20assigning%20any%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20three%20judge%20bench%20passed%20a%20cryptic%20and%20perfunctory%20order%20without%20assigning%20any%20reasons.%20Doctrine%20of%20precedents%20is%20the%20core%20value%20of%20our%20legal%20system.%20In%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20reference%20was%20made%20to%20reconsider%20EV%20Chinnaiah%20without%20any%20reasons%20and%20that%20too%20after%2015%20years%20of%20the%20judgment.%20The%20very%20reference%20was%20itself%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20any%20sub-classification%20in%20backward%20communities%20will%20have%20to%20be%20determined%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20empirical%20data%20to%20show%20that%20there%20is%20an%20inadequacy%20of%20representation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722496680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fa1ooga8_supreme-court-of-india_650x400_14_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-okays-separate-quotas-for-marginalised-among-sc-sts-6237025%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20seven-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20okayed%20subclassification%20within%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20categories%20to%20provide%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%20for%20the%20more%20marginalised%20among%20backward%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-okays-separate-quotas-for-marginalised-among-sc-sts-6237025%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-okays-separate-quotas-for-marginalised-among-sc-sts-6237025%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-okays-separate-quotas-for-marginalised-among-sc-sts-6237025%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Grant%20Bail%20To%20Killers%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20Bail%20Plea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20issued%20notice%20to%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20a%20bail%20plea%20filed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbibhav-kumar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBibhav%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20aide%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20boss%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20arrested%20in%20May%2