s%20were%20recovered%20about%20500%20m%20away%2C%20the%20mother%20still%20clutching%20her%20son's%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20family%20members%20have%20said%20the%20mother%20and%20son%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20if%20the%20rescue%20operation%20was%20swift.%20Her%20husband%20Govind%20Singh%2C%20who%20works%20in%20a%20private%20firm%20in%20Noida%2C%20was%20at%20work%20when%20disaster%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20rescue%20operation%20was%20swift%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20son%20could%20have%20been%20saved.%20Every%20year%2C%20such%20incidents%20take%20place%2C%20but%20no%20action%20is%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanuja's%20uncle%20Harish%20Rawat%20said%20the%20drain%20was%20overflowing%20and%20she%20could%20not%20spot%20it%20in%20time.%20%26quot%3BWe%20got%20information%20around%207.30%20pm.%20We%20dialled%20100%20and%20the%20cops%20came%20with%20a%20rescue%20team.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20have%20proper%20equipment.%20They%20kept%20trying%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20work.%20The%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20rushed%20Tanuja%20and%20Priyansh%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20a%20private%20cab%2C%20hoping%20against%20hope%20that%20they%20will%20make%20it.%20%26quot%3BWe%20took%20them%20to%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20Hospital.%20No%20ambulance%20was%20arranged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rawat%20said%20Tanuja%2C%20even%20in%20death%2C%20did%20not%20leave%20her%20son's%20hand.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20body%20was%20found%2C%20she%20was%20still%20holding%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20residents%20slammed%20civic%20authorities%2C%20saying%20that%20this%20drain%20has%20been%20open%20for%20the%20past%20three%20months%20and%20overflows%20during%20every%20spell%20of%20rain.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20complained%20multiple%20times%2C%20but%20the%20administration%20does%20not%20want%20to%20work.%20I%20have%