uly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722495055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F28%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1716919563-9456.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fsofter-increase-in-new-orders-output-slows-jul-manufacturing-pmi-to-58-1-124080100435_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22However%2C%20international%20sales%20expanded%20at%20the%20fastest%20pace%20in%20over%2013%20years%2C%20while%20job%20creation%20remained%20robust%2C%20and%20selling%20prices%20saw%20the%20steepest%20increase%20since%20October%202013%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fsofter-increase-in-new-orders-output-slows-jul-manufacturing-pmi-to-58-1-124080100435_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fsofter-increase-in-new-orders-output-slows-jul-manufacturing-pmi-to-58-1-124080100435_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fsofter-increase-in-new-orders-output-slows-jul-manufacturing-pmi-to-58-1-124080100435_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPolicy%20To%20Identify%20Creamy%20Layer%20Must%26quot%3B%3A%20Judge's%20Big%20Remark%20In%20Quota%20Ruling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20landmark%20judgment%20clearing%20sub-classification%20within%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20to%20extend%20reservation%20to%20the%20more%20marginalised%2C%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20said%20the%20State%20must%20come%20up%20with%20a%20policy%20to%20identify%20the%20creamy%20layer%20among%20these%20communities%20and%20take%20them%20out%20of%20the%20fold%20of%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gavai%20is%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%20and%20is%20set%20to%20become%20Chief%20Justice%20next%20year.%20He%20will%20be%20the%20second%20Dalit%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20after%20KG%20Balakrishnan.%20In%20today's%20judgment%2C%20he%20made%20strong%20observations%20on%20how%20people%20from%20the%20creamy%20layer%20of%20backward%20communities%20were%20cornering%20quota%20benefits%20and%20depriving%20the%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20person%20gets%20into%20a%20compartment%2C%20he%20tries%20all%20means%20to%20stop%20others%20from%20getting%20into%20that%20compartment.%20Only%20on%20account%20of%20social%20justice%20they%20have%20got%20the%20benefit%2C%20but%20when%20state%20decides%20to%20give%20that%20benefit%20to%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20not%20adequately%20represented%2C%20then%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20denied%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BState%20must%20evolve%20a%20policy%20to%20identify%20creamy%20layer%20among%20the%20SC%2FST%20category%20and%20take%20them%20out%20of%20the%20fold%20of%20affirmative%20action.%20This%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20gain%20true%20equality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20referred%20to%20a%20speech%20by%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20in%201949%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20political%20democracy%20cannot%20last%20unless%20social%20democracy%20is%20at%20the%20base%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20section%20within%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20are%20enjoying%20the%20benefits%20of%20reservation.%20The%20ground%20reality%20cannot%20be%20denied%20that%20there%20are%20classes%20within%20SC%2FST%20communities%20that%20are%20facing%20harassment.%20The%20basis%20of%20sub-classification%20is%20that%20a%20large%20section%20is%20facing%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20noted%20that%20comparing%20a%20child%20from%20the%20creamy%20layer%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20with%20a%20child%20from%20the%20same%20community%20who%20picks%20rags%20in%20a%20village%20would%20amount%20to%20%26quot%3Bcheating%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20other%20judges%20on%20the%20seven-judge%20bench%20agreed%20to%20Justice%20Gavai's%20position%20on%20the%20creamy%20layer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Pankaj%20Mithal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BReservation%20should%20be%20meant%20for%20only%20the%20first%20generation%20among%20a%20category.%20If%20the%20second%20generation%20has%20come%20up%2C%20then%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20shall%20not%20be%20given.%20The%20State%20should%20see%20if%2C%20after%20reservation%2C%20the%20second%20generation%20has%20come%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20with%20the%20general%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20SC%20Sharma%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BThe%20identification%20of%20creamy%20layer%20among%20SC%2F%20STs%20must%20become%20a%20Constitutional%20imperative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Vikram%20Nath%20said%20that%20creamy%20layer%20principle%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20OBC%20communities%2C%20must%20apply%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722495000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc1vrcv3g_justice-gavai-at-columbia-law-school-ndtv_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-justice-br-gavai-policy-to-identify-creamy-layer-must-judges-big-remark-in-quota-ruling-6237545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delivering%20the%20landmark%20judgment%20clearing%20sub-classification%20within%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20to%20extend%20reservation%20to%20the%20more%20marginalised%2C%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20said%20the%20State%20must%20come%20up%20with%20a%20policy%20to%20identify%20the%20creamy%20layer%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-justice-br-gavai-policy-to-identify-creamy-layer-must-judges-big-remark-in-quot