Laurels%20At%204%20Academic%20Olympiads%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20student%20contingents%20have%20emerged%20with%20flying%20colours%20at%20prestigious%20international%20Olympiads%20in%20Biology%2C%20Maths%2C%20Physics%20and%20Chemistry%20held%20this%20month%2C%20earning%20plaudits%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20other%20bigwigs%2C%20officials%20said%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20participating%20teams%20went%20through%20the%20Homi%20Bhabha%20Centre%20for%20Science%20Education%20(HBCSE)%20of%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Fundamental%20Research%20(TIFR)%20here%20and%20bagged%20several%20medals%20and%20honours%20for%20the%20country%2C%20including%20seven%20won%20by%20Maharashtra%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20the%2035th%20International%20Biology%20Olympiad%20(IBO%20%E2%80%93%20July%207-13)%20held%20in%20Astana%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Kazakhstan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20bagged%20one%20gold%20(Vedant%20Sakre%20of%20Mumbai)%20and%20three%20silvers%20(Ishan%20Pednekar%20of%20Ratnagiri%3B%20Shrijith%20Sivakumar%20of%20Chennai%20and%20Yashaswi%20Kumar%20of%20Bareilly).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20the%2065th%20International%20Mathematical%20Olympiad%20(IMO%20%E2%80%93%20July%2011-22)%20held%20in%20Bath%2C%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingents%20bagged%20four%20golds%20(Adhitya%20M.%20V.%20Ganesh%20of%20Pune%3B%20Kanav%20Talwar%20of%20Greater%20NOIDA%3B%20Rushil%20Mathur%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20Anando%20Bhadur%20of%20Guwahati)%2C%20while%20Arjun%20Gupta%20of%20Delhi%20got%20a%20silver%20medal%20and%20Siddharth%20Choppara%20of%20Pune%20secured%20an%20Honourable%20Mention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20was%20the%2054th%20International%20Physics%20Olympiad%20(IPhO%20%E2%80%93%20July%2021-29)%2C%20held%20in%20Isfahan%2C%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20secured%202%20golds%20(Rhythm%20Kedia%20of%20Raipur%20and%20Ved%20Lahoti%20of%20Indore)%2C%20plus%203%20silvers%20(Akarshraj%20Sahay%20of%20Nagpur%3B%20Bhavya%20Tiwari%20of%20NOIDA%20and%20Jaiveer%20Singh%20of%20Kota).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%2056th%20International%20Chemistry%20Olympiad%20(IchO%20%E2%80%93%20July%2021-30)%20was%20held%20in%20Riyadh%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingent%20secured%20a%20gold%20(Devesh%20P.%20Bhaiya%20of%20Jalgaon)%2C%202%20silvers%20(Avaneesh%20Bansal%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20Harshin%20Posina%20of%20Hyderabad)%20while%20Kashyap%20Khandelwal%20of%20Mumbai%20got%20a%20bronze%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai-based%20HBCSE%20-%20a%20national%20centre%20of%20the%20TIFR%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20premier%20institution%20for%20research%20and%20development%20in%20science%2C%20technology%20and%20mathematics%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20India's%20nodal%20centre%20or%20Olympiad%20programmes%20in%20mathematics%2C%20physics%2C%20chemistry%2C%20biology%2C%20astronomy%20and%20junior%20sciences%20which%20attract%20the%20participation%20of%20students%20from%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722491340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fj72kpjp_indian-students-at-olympiad_625x300_31_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-students-win-laurels-at-4-academic-olympiads-6230827%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20student%20contingents%20have%20emerged%20with%20flying%20colours%20at%20prestigious%20international%20Olympiads%20in%20Biology%2C%20Maths%2C%20Physics%20and%20Chemistry%20held%20this%20month%2C%20earning%20plaudits%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20other%20bigwigs%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-students-win-laurels-at-4-academic-olympiads-6230827%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-students-win-laurels-at-4-academic-olympiads-6230827%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-students-win-laurels-at-4-academic-olympiads-6230827%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTime%20Thoda%20Lagta%20Hai%26quot%3B%3A%20Dhoni%20Finally%20Opens%20Up%20On%202019%20WC%20Heartbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20suffered%20a%20bitter%20semi-final%20defeat%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20The%20result%20continued%20to%20bother%20Indian%20fans%20all%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20team%20had%20done%20wonders%20until%20the%20penultimate%20hurdle.%20Many%20still%20wonder%20what%20the%20result%20would've%20been%20if%20New%20Zealand's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Martin%20Guptill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1225-martin-guptill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMartin%20Guptill%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20not%20run%20out%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20match.%20The%20contest%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20MS%20Dhoni's%20last%20as%20he%20chose%20to%20hang%20up%20his%20boots%20from%20international%20cricket%20a%20few%20months%20after%20the%20event%20ended.%20Years%20have%20passed%20since%20the%20infamous%20heartbreak%2C%20and%20Dhoni%20has%20finally%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20pain%20of%20failure%20to%20not%20lift%20the%20title%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20that%20has%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Dhoni%20could%20be%20heard%20recalling%20the%20disappointment%2C%20saying%20it%20took%20some%20time%20for%20him%20to%20get%20over%20the%20pain%20of%20losing%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20difficult%20one%20because%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20will%20be%20my%20last%20World%20Cup%2C%20so%20it%20would%20have%20been%20good%20to%20be%20on%20the%20winning%20side.%20It%20was%20heartbreak%20moment%2C%20so%20we%20accepted%20the%20result%20and%20we%20tried%20to%20move%20on.%20%3Cem%3ETime%20thoda%20lagta%20hai%20aur%20World%20Cup%20ke%20baad%20thoda%20time%20mil%20bhi%20jata%20hai.%20Maine%20toh%20uske%20baad%20international%20khela%20nahi%20hai%20toh%20mujhe%20toh%20kaafi%20time%20mila%20hai.%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%20takes%20time%20and%20one%20gets%20some%20time%20after%20the%20World%20Cup.%20I%20haven't%20played%20any%20international%20after%20that%2C%20so%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20time).%20So%2C%20yes%2C%20it%20was%20a%20heartbreak%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20you%20have%20to%20get%20out%20of%20it.%20So%20you%20just%20accept%20that%20you%20tried%20your%20best%2C%20but%20you%20were%20not%20able%20to%20win%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%20On%202019%20World%20Cup%20Semi%20Final%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMSDhoni%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MSDhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHAiXWBivef%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHAiXWBivef%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Chakri%20Dhoni%20(%40ChakriDhonii)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChakriDhonii%2Fstatus%2F1818685384563605604%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dhoni%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20international%20cricketer%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20play%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20for%20his%20franchise%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%20His%20participation%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20season%2C%20however%2C