0course%20in%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20costs%20Rs%20500%20per%20girl.%20Currently%2C%20she%20has%2020%20students%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20teaching%20these%20enthusiastic%20young%20girls%20is%20a%20joyful%20experience%2C%20what%20gives%20Rachna%20immense%20pride%20is%20being%20chosen%20as%20a%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20trainer%20in%20February%202024%20by%20the%20foundation.%20After%20being%20a%20trainee%20under%20this%20project%20to%20now%20becoming%20its%20paid%20trainer%2C%20Rachna%E2%80%99s%20life%20has%20come%20full%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPaving%20a%20path%20for%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20Rachna%20almost%208-10%20hours%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20The%20price%20of%20each%20framed%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20ranges%20from%20Rs%201%2C000-3%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20intricacy%20of%20work%20and%20its%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20part%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20sale%20is%20spent%20on%20raw%20material%20like%20wheat%20stalks%2C%20paying%20shop%20rent%20and%20electricity%20bills%2C%20Rachna%20is%20using%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20money%20to%20fund%20her%20dream%20to%20continue%20her%20education.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20it%20was%20Rachna%E2%80%99s%20success%20story%20that%20inspired%20most%20of%20these%20students%20to%20join%20her%20classes.%20When%20Pooja%20(17)%20heard%20about%20how%20Rachna%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267937%2Fmenstrual-health-period-poverty-delhi-pinkishe-social-impact-facebook-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20her%20life%20around%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20her%20painting%20and%20entrepreneurial%20skills%2C%20she%20was%20keen%20to%20do%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202016px)%20100vw%2C%202016px%