0on%20Facebook%20where%20Rachna%20posts%20the%20photos%20of%20her%20paintings.%20She%20was%20so%20motivated%20that%20she%20walked%208%20km%20from%20her%20village%20to%20Rachna%E2%80%99s%20shop%20to%20learn%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20wheat%20stalk%20paintings%20has%20increased%20since%20it%20was%20chosen%20to%20represent%20Bahraich%20under%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20One%20District%2C%20One%20Product%20programme.%20Launched%20in%202018%2C%20its%20goal%20is%20to%20encourage%20greater%20visibility%20and%20sale%20of%20indigenous%20and%20specialised%20products%20of%20each%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonika%20Rani%2C%20the%20district%20magistrate%20of%20Bahraich%2C%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%20through%20education%20and%20livelihood%20training.%20%E2%80%9CRachna%20is%20proving%20that%20given%20the%20opportunity%20and%20skills%2C%20girls%20can%20overcome%20all%20obstacles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPicture%20courtesy%3A%20Swapna%20Majumdar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722316027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wheat%20stalk%20painting%2C%20a%20traditional%20art%20form%20of%20Bahraich%2C%20is%20a%20laborious%20and%20time%20consuming%20process.%20Here's%20how%20it%20is%20helping%20girls%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20fight%20the%20clutches%20of%20early%20marriage%20and%20work%20towards%20financial%20independence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Swapna%20Majumdar%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358515%2Fwheat-stalk-painting-from-bahraich-uttar-pradesh-girls-training-early-marriage-entrepreneurship%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CA%20Final%202024%3A%20Siblings%20With%20AIR%201%20and%2018%20Share%20Preparation%20Tips%2C%20Planning%20Secrets%20%26amp%3B%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20can%20be%20divided%20into%20two%20sets%20of%20people%3A%20those%20who%20like%20to%20study%20alone%20and%20those%20who%20prefer%20a%20study%20buddy.%20I%20fall%20into%20the%20latter%20category%2C%20as%20having%20someone%20in%20the%20same%20boat%20as%20you%20to%20motivate%20you%20and%20answer%20your%20queries%20is%20a%20boon.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20fun%2C%20as%20you%20have%20someone%20to%20discuss%20doubts%20with%20during%20break%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20if%20this%20study%20buddy%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20house%E2%80%94your%20sibling%3F%20This%20is%20usually%20a%20rarity%20unless%20the%20sibling%20is%20a%20twin%2C%20but%20these%20siblings%20from%20Morena%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349546%2Fakshata-krishnamurthy-nasa-aerospace-engineer-rocket-scientist-space-career-mit%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheights%20that%20can%20be%20achieved%20together.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20(24)%20and%20Nandini%20(22)%20Agrawal%2C%20although%20two%20years%20apart%2C%20were%20in%20the%20same%20class%20since%20Class%202.%20Nandini%20skipped%20two%20classes%20and%20joined%20her%20brother%20in%20his%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20paths%20intertwined%20as%20they%20decided%20on%20a%20singular%20goal%3A%20to%20add%20two%20letters%20before%20their%20name%20%E2%80%94%20CA%20(Chartered%20Accountant).%20The%20duo%20worked%20together%20towards%20achieving%20this%20goal%2C%20choosing%20the%20same%20coaching%20class%20and%20the%20same%20city%20for%20their%20articleships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20how!%20Both%20of%20them%20achieved%20ranks%20in%20the%20CA%20Final%20in%202021.%20The%20icing%20on%20the%2