%99%2C%20and%20eventually%20open%20her%20own%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20Today%2C%20she%20offers%20over%20250%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300822%2Fsenior-citizen-entrepreneur-sheila-pickles-jams-traditional-kerala-recipes-home-business-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarieties%20of%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20herbal%20juices%2C%20chutneys%2C%20marmalades%2C%20and%20syrups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358853%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKrishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Rohilla%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20for%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20pickles%20perfectly%20capture%20the%20essence%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomemade%20goodness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20offering%20a%20nostalgic%20taste.%20Their%20wide%20variety%20of%20flavours%20caters%20to%20every%20palate%20and%20mood.%20Whenever%20I%20open%20one%20of%20their%20jars%2C%20it%20bursts%20with%20authentic%20tastes%20and%20aromas%2C%20enhancing%20my%20simple%20meals.%20These%20pickles%20never%20disappoint%2C%20consistently%20maintaining%20their%20taste%20and%20quality%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20has%20established%20a%20five-storey%20facility%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20manufactures%2010%20to%2020%20quintals%20of%20pickles%20daily%2C%20and%20her%20company%20boasts%20an%20impressive%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20extraordinary%20determination%20and%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%2C%20she%20has%20been%20recognised%20with%20multiple%20awards%20including%20the%20Outstanding%20Women%20Award%20from%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%202012%3B%20the%20Innovative%20Award%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20allied%20activities%20during%20the%20Global%20Agriculture%20Summit%202013%3B%20and%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Award%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20homemaker%20and%20my%20core%20job%20was%20to%20look%20after%20the%20household%20duties.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20family%20income%20in%20our%20dire%20times.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20let%20my%20children%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20our%20financial%20crisis.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20and%20I%20never%20imagined%20I%20would%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20eldest%20son%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20business%2C%20while%20her%20other%20two%20children%20are%20currently%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20have%20both%20%3Cem%3Egaadi%20bangla%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20car%20and%20a%20bungalow)%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20dignity%20to%20walk%20with%20pride.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20on%20television%2C%20and%20that%20dream%20came%20true%20with%20my%20business.%20However%2C%20achieving%20this%20success%20required%20consistent%20hard%20work.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20stop%20now%2C%20I%20would%20risk%20losing%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20example%2C%20Krishna%20emphasises%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20adversity%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20resilience.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20be%20bogged%20down%20by%20failures.%20Do%20not%20view%20helplessness%20or%20failure%20as%20a%20setback%20but%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20greater%20achievements.%20If%20one%20door%20closes%2C%20many%20others%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722240366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Krishna%20Yadav%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20began%20selling%20pickles%20on%20the%20roadside.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20established%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20growing%20her%20business%20into%20a%20successful%20enterprise%20with%20over%20250%20varieties%20of%20products%20and%20a%20five-storey%20factory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358846%2Futtar-pradesh-krishna-yadav-pickle-business-delhi-earn-crores-woman-empowerment%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Built%20By%2090%20People%20From%2018%20Countries%2C%20%E2%80%98Fairytale%E2%80%99%20Home%20in%20Rishikesh%20Was%20Made%20to%20Escape%20Cities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20replica%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask%20Raghav%20Kumar%20(30)%2C%20one%20half%20of%20the%20brother%20duo%20that%20has%20conceptualised%20a%20600-sq%20ft%20beauty%20in%20the%20heartland%20of%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand.%20As%20fans%20of%20the%20seven-part%20fantasy%20series%20%E2%80%98Harry%20Potter%E2%80%99%20will%20immediately%20guess%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20referring%20to%20the%20eight-foot-tall%20giant%20Rubeus%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20cabin%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20The%20Forbidden%20Forest%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ominous%20wood%20filled%20with%20wizarding%20creatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosy%20fires%2C%20larger-than-life%20teacups%2C%20and%20a%20drooling%20boarhound%20Fang%20filled%20most%20evenings%20that%20Harry%20and%20his%20friends%20spent%20at%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s.%20I%20often%20found%20myself%20craving%20to%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wish%20might%20just%20have%20been%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20and%20Ansh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%E2%80%99%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20abode.%20Creating%20the%2015-ft%20doppelganger%20homestay%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20goal%20that%20backed%20their%20transition%20from%20their%20city%20life%20in%20Delhi%20to%20the%20mountains%20in%202021.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20a%20consequence%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20architects%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20(27)%20were%20keen%20on%20living%20an%20%E2%80%9Cintentional%20life%20closer%20to%20nature%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dream%20they%20felt%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20achieved%20by%20being%20a%20part%20of%20modern%20corporate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247572%2Fmaharashtra-ecofriendly-green-architecture-domes-arches-cost-effective-sustainable-homes-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20prized%20demand%20over%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20disconnect%20between%20the%20architect%20and%20the%20labour%20involved%20in%20these%20projects.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20greenwashing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghav%20notes.%20Prior%20to%202021%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20boys%20had%20their%20week%20cut%20out%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20weekdays%20spent%20working%20long%20hours%20and%20weekends%20trekking%20to%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9_3aPdHLQ9Y%3Fsi%3DuSBCfoXQnBlYuCgm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20for%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20was%20sown%20when%2C%20after%20one%20particular%20trek%20to%20Rishikesh%20in%20December%202020%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20found%20themselves%20wishing%20they%20could%20stay%20back%20in%20the%20mountains%20and%20not%20return%20to%20the%20monotonous%20hustle.%20And%20they%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20completely%20bewildered%20by%20topics%20of%20gardening%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189744%2Fbangalore-lifestyle-one-day-holiday-village-rural-pottery-green-trip-village-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20rural%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20of%20building%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20has%20stretched%20their%20understanding%20in%20these%20regards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20invite%20us%20