otor%20skills%20among%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemarkably%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20also%20noted%20the%20therapeutic%20benefits%20of%20weaving%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262932%2Fautism-guardian-village-residential-space-community-hyderabad%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20with%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20an%20account%20of%20a%20mother%20and%20her%20child%20with%20%E2%80%98special%20needs%E2%80%99%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mother%20informed%20me%20that%20her%20child%20cannot%20sit%20still%20in%20one%20place%20for%20more%20than%20three%20minutes.%20She%20was%20very%20afraid%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20taking%20him%20to%20learn%20weaving%2C%20a%20skill%20that%20requires%20focus%20and%20attention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20the%20first%20five%20minutes%2C%20the%20child%20found%20the%20work%20engaging%20and%20continued%20to%20weave%20for%20half%20an%20hour%20without%20getting%20distracted.%20His%20mother%20became%20so%20overwhelmed%20to%20see%20this%20that%20she%20broke%20down.%20The%20kid%20had%20anger%20or%20temperamental%20issues%20but%20weaving%20provided%20him%20calmness.%20This%20gave%20me%20an%20idea%20to%20introduce%20DIY%20kits%20as%20occupational%20therapy%20for%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20has%20already%20gained%20traction%20with%2010%20schools%20showing%20interest%20in%20including%20weaving%20as%20part%20of%20their%20curriculum%2C%20alongside%20partnerships%20for%20homeschooling%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20textile%20exhibitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kalaiyarasi%2C%20this%20venture%20is%20not%20just%20a%20business%20but%20a%20heartfelt%20mission%20to%20contribute%20to%20society.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20only%20doing%20the%20business%20but%20we%20are%20doing%20something%20fo